[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     50[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### W1. `coach_full_pipeline` invokes `handle_conversation` twice per inbound message because `receive_message` already terminates by `return handle_conversation(...)`; the demo inflates the tool-call ledger by 2x and pays for double LLM invocations per turn
