[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    497[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    498[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### N8. The Pinpoint `Addresses` keys use synthetic `f"endpoint-{patient_id}"` strings rather than real channel addresses (phone numbers for SMS, push tokens for GCM); a learner copying this hits Pinpoint validation errors against a real campaign
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    499[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
